Package client

Class Config

java.lang.Object
client.Config
public class Config extends Object
Config is a utility class used for configuration of app set up. It will set the up in accordance to set up choise. Choosing 'EK' for set up the system in a store. Choosing 'OL' for set up the system to users private use.
